------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Lesson 17 语法讲解

+ 名词的单复数
    books   jobs
    buses boxes brushes benches benches ptatoes
    wives   leaves
    babies
    men

+ 句的复数

    单数名词 + is...
    复数名词 + are...

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Lesson 17 课文讲解

+ 打招呼
    Hello
    How are you?
    How are you doing?

    How do you do?
    幸会

+ Come and meet             过来看看...
+ Come and sit down.        过来坐坐
+ What are their jobs?
+ What is your job?

+ 单词的复数&句子的复数

    This is my name.
    These are theirs names.

    句子的复数形式需要考虑代词、动词、名词的一致.

    Who is the yong girl?
    Who are the yong girls?
